 Zahara, real name Bulelwa Mkutukana, is over R350000 in arrears after failing to pay for her Audi A5 drop-top she bought through Wesbank when she was still a TS Records artist about three years ago. An accountant who saw the account said Zahara bought the road monster in August 2012 for over R620000 and was supposed to pay more than R12000 in monthly instalments. GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY